Blocks.Text: Mr. Copthome knew a way round by the side
of the church where there was & small Open
outhidding where the grave digger kept his spades
and forts and tidying up implements. It might
be open It was. He entered, and reated himself
in a huddle upon an upturned wheelbarrow.
this curious headgea, fell off Strange things
were going on in his bewildered brain When
a man was drowning and towards his last
gasp it was scientifically supposed his whole
